machine (VM) instance through its internal IP address:
<https://cloud.google.com/compute/docs/connect/ssh-internal-ip>
{% endblock default_ingress_failure_reason %}

{% block default_ingress_failure_remediation %}
If connecting to a non-public VM and do not wish to allow external access, choose one of the following connection
options for VMs
<https://cloud.google.com/compute/docs/connect/ssh-internal-ip>
Alternatively, create/update a firewall rule to allow access
<https://cloud.google.com/firewall/docs/using-firewalls#creating_firewall_rules>
{% endblock default_ingress_failure_remediation %}

